---
import Layout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';

const metadata = {
  title: 'Experience — Demetri Williams',
};
---

<Layout metadata={metadata}>
  <section class="px-6 py-12 max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2">Experience</h1>
    <p class="text-muted mb-10">My professional background in AI training, quality assurance, and software engineering.</p>

    <div class="mb-12 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-1">AI Trainer / QA Analyst</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-400 font-medium mb-1">TELUS Digital — Remote</p>
      <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">July 2025 – September 2025</p>
      <ul class="text-muted space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Trained image recognition models by reviewing large-scale image datasets and correcting classifications to improve operational accuracy and reliability of computer vision systems.</li>
        <li>Performed diagnostic analysis to identify error sources, reduce misclassification rates, and improve training efficiency.</li>
        <li>Provided actionable recommendations for process improvement across analytics workflows.</li>
        <li>Documented training processes and outcomes via detailed reports and tracking metrics to support transparency, reproducibility, and continuous improvement in AI development.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-1">AI Training Specialist / Generalist</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-400 font-medium mb-1">Outlier AI — Remote</p>
      <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">May 2024 – December 2024</p>
      <ul class="text-muted space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Conducted performance analysis and proofread AI outputs by reviewing model responses daily, ensuring accuracy and alignment with expected solutions.</li>
        <li>Led root cause analysis on errors, identifying patterns in outputs and highlighting common trends.</li>
        <li>Trained and fine-tuned AI models using real-world datasets and feedback loops to enhance problem-solving capabilities and consistency.</li>
        <li>Collaborated with team members nationally and internationally to maximize cross-functional teamwork and operational excellence.</li>
        <li>Prepared descriptive data reports and submitted them to engineers nationally and internationally.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12 border-l-4 border-blue-500 pl-6">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-1">B.S. Computer Science Engineering</h2>
      <p class="text-blue-400 font-medium mb-1">Louisiana State University (LSU) — Baton Rouge, LA</p>
      <p class="text-muted text-sm mb-4">Expected May 2027</p>
      <ul class="text-muted space-y-2 list-disc list-inside">
        <li>Concentration in Software Engineering. GPA: 3.25.</li>
        <li>Dean's List 2025. Summer Student 2025 (4.0 GPA).</li>
        <li>Relevant coursework: Artificial Intelligence, Database Systems, Software Systems, Advanced Data Structures & Algorithms, Programming Languages, Introduction to Cloud Computing, Operating Systems, Systems Programming, Object Oriented Design, and many others.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>